➜苏坛：《期待》
http://www.sohu.com/a/431979823_100115135	27547
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201115/39f0161338694d8795ad8a5c9fa65aa7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《期待》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/苏坛</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">期待着来年的重缝</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也想再一次目睹你的芳容</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">想紧紧握住你的手</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">更想举杯畅饮</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让友谊激荡在胸口</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>总是幻想着走遍千山万水</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>期待在一个彼此陌生的地方</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>意外重缝</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>想和你热情拥抱一下</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>可爱的话语却止步在喉咙口</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人生啊！有多少美好的回忆</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如清风轻轻吹入转角的巷口</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因为彼此的牵挂</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我关注你书写着华彩风流</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>我们都不想轻言忘记</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>更不愿友情断流</strong></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
